thread.title: Planemakers look at higher output to meet demand

title: Planemakers look at higher output to meet demand
text:
Planemakers look at higher output to meet demand 12:32pm EST - 01:42 
The world's largest planemakers signalled a possible increase in output of their most popular passenger jets on Tuesday, highlighting their confidence about growth in demand for air travel. Kate King reports.
